http://www.free-eco.org:80/free/ST94/ExportBan2.html 204.71.237.97 19970117032150 text/html 7168
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Friday, 17-Jan-97 03:21:56 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 01-Jul-96 01:17:00 GMT
Content-length: 6985
Content-type: text/html
