http://www.free-eco.org:80/free/ST94/Socialist94.html 204.71.237.97 19970117032322 text/html 6543
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Friday, 17-Jan-97 03:23:34 GMT
