http://www.free-eco.org:80/free/ST94/Downsizing94.html 204.71.237.97 19970117032701 text/html 7025
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Friday, 17-Jan-97 03:27:17 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 01-Jul-96 01:16:28 GMT
Content-length: 6842
