http://www.free-eco.org:80/free/ST95/Beltway.ST1995.html 204.71.237.97 19970117025444 text/html 7499
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Friday, 17-Jan-97 02:54:54 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 01-Jul-96 01:18:46 GMT
Content-length: 7316
Content-type: text/html
