<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
<p><font color="#408080"><font size=6><strong>Welcome To Auburn!</strong></font></font></p>
<hr>
<p>Our wish is to make Auburn Drive a new school with new ideas and we have accomplished a 
great deal in the first few years. What we do in coming years will largely depend on our ability to 
work together and as Henry For once said,&quot;Coming together is a beginning, keeping together is 
progress, working together is success.&quot; This is the challenge for us in the years to come.</p>
