<DOCHDR>
http://www.adhs.ednet.ns.ca:80/newideas.htm 142.227.165.2 19970222014158 text/html 3384
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Saturday, 22-Feb-97 01:36:46 GMT
Server: FrontPage-PWS32/1.1.2.6
