<head>
<title>Mission Statement</title>
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
</head>

<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
<p align=left><font color="#408080"><font size=6><strong>Our Mission Statement:</strong></font></font><font color="#FFFFFF"><font size=7><strong> </strong></font></font></p>
<hr>
<p><font color="#00000B"><font size=4>The mission of Auburn Drive as a technologically advanced and innovated 
high school is to develop versatile, competent and responsible citizens instilled 
with a commitment to continued personal growth, capable of progressing in an 
ever changing society by integrating the diverse resources of the individual, the 
school, business and the community.</font></font></p>
