   <META NAME="description" CONTENT="Select Timing Service (STS) is a short-term mutual fund switching system that has shown great promise: in 8 years of rigorous historical testing and real-time trading it generates over 1000% return on equity -- equivalent to over 36% average annualized return. What's more, these returns were achieved with a low downside volatity.">
