<CENTER><P><A NAME="maintop"></A><IMG SRC="timelab.gif" ALT="STS Picture: Timepiece" HEIGHT=180 WIDTH=240></P></CENTER>

<CENTER><P> </P></CENTER>

<H3><A HREF="about.htm">Timing Laboratory</A> and <A HREF="about.htm#DlinkSoft">DollarLink
Software</A></H3>

<P><I>present</I> </P>

<H1 ALIGN=CENTER>Select Timing Service</H1>

<CENTER><P><IMG SRC="saturn.gif" ALT="rotating rings of Saturn" HEIGHT=24 WIDTH=34></P></CENTER>

<CENTER><P> </P></CENTER>

<CENTER><P><IMG SRC="stripe.gif" ALT="----------------------------------" HEIGHT=4 WIDTH=540>
</P></CENTER>

<P><B>Select Timing Service (STS) is a short-term mutual fund switching
system that has shown very good results: in 8 years of rigorous historical
testing <I>and</I> real-time trading it generates over 900% return on equity
-- equivalent to 34% average compounded annualized return. What's more,
these returns were achieved with a low downside volatity.</B></P>

<P>

