<DOCNO>WT05-B02-155</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA064-000376-B037-107</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://dollarlink.com:80/details.htm 207.137.200.123 19970112081311 text/html 11907
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
