<h1>About DollarWin</h1>        
<IMG SRC="stripe.gif" ALT="----------------------------------"><p>

DollarWin is an electronic newsletter that specializes in mutual fund
switching using a momentum-based technical analysis method.  The model
portfolios recommended by DollarWin have done very well in 1995: up about 45%
on the average.<p>

DollarWin is <img src="new.gif" alt="New! ">E-mailed daily on the Internet <img src="new.gif" alt="New! ">
or broadcast daily by the <a href="http://www.dbc.com">DBC-Signal</a> datafeed as a
Signal Report.<p>

If you are interested in <a href="dwini.htm">getting DollarWin-on-Internet</a>, please click 
<a href="dwini.htm">here </a> to learn about pricing and terms.<p>

<!-- Click <a href="http://www.vestnet.com/nl-sts/dlr_about.html">here</a> -->
