<title>How To Join Pit-Stop.</title>
</head>
<body background="chalk.jpg">
<center><h1><img src="flag.gif">How To Join Pit-Stop<img src="flag.gif"></h1></center>
<hr size=6>
<ADDRESS><b>Requirements to advertise with Pit-Stop Internet, Ltd.</b> Your web page <b>must</b> be related to the automotive industry. The automotive industry includes all automotive related clubs and associations, repair shops, parts stores, warehouses 

and Automobile dealerships. If you would like to join, contact us and one of our representitives will be happy to assist you with any of your needs.
</ADDRESS>
<hr size=6>
<CENTER>
