<BODY BACKGROUND="chalk.jpg">
<H1><CENTER><img src="flag.gif">What is the Pit-Crew up to next?<img 
src="flag.gif"></CENTER></H1> <HR SIZE=6>

<center>
<table border>
<tr><td><CENTER><IMG SRC="banner.jpg"></CENTER><BR>
<CENTER><A><font color="GREEN">Adding the option to create VRML web pages for our clients.</font></A></CENTER><BR>
<CENTER><A><font color="RED"><BLINK>Imagine...Driving a race car at a Virtual Race Track!!!</BLINK></font></A></CENTER>
</td></tr>
</table>
</center>
<p>
<center>
<table border>
<tr><td>
<CENTER><IMG SRC="java.jpg"></CENTER>
<CENTER><A>Adding Java to our pages and our clients' pages.</A></CENTER>
</td></tr>
</table>
</center>
<p>
<center>
<table border>
<tr><td>
<li><b><font color="RED">Scouring the Internet for ANY AUTO ENTHUSIAST 
CLUB ON THE WEB, to put links here, for your convenience! This 
is such a large task that our initial focus is on SPORTS CAR 
related clubs and activities.</font></b><br>
<li><b><font color="RED">Combing the Web and the World to build the 
definitive, on-line, data resource of race track maps and 
information!</font></b><br> </td></tr>
</table>
</center>
