alink="#FF0000" background="bkggy.gif">

<center><p><img src="pitlogo.gif" border=0 height=99 width=300></p></center>

<center><p><b><font SIZE=+2>Contract for Hosting Services</font></b></p></center>

<center><p>
<hr width="100%" ></p></center>

<p><b><font SIZE=+1>We (Pit-Stop Internet, Ltd.) agree to:</font></b></p>

<p>1. Set up your web page (.HTML-based) on our server within 48 hours of
its availability to us at our site as an E-mail transmission with a PKZip-compressed
attachment.</p>

<p>2. Notify you of your WWW address within 24 hours of setting up
the page.</p>

<p>3. Prepare and transmit within 24 houss, registration data for your
page with the major internet search engines.</p>

<p>4. Provide one free monthly maintenance of the site.</p>

<p>5. Make available to you statistics on web page activity.</p>

<p>6. Actively promote <b>(Pit-Stop Internet, Ltd.)</b>, the 
<b>&quot;Electronic Garage&quot;</b>,
and the clients hosted on it through appropriate media.On a selective basis,
feature articles about hosted clients in a &quot;News&quot; page on the
<b>Pit-Stop&copy;</b>.</p>

<p><b><font SIZE=+1>You (the Client, signed below) agree to:</font></b></p>

<p>1. Provide us with your developed web page ready for server installation
in a timely manner.</p>

<p>2. Review the page after notification from us that it is available for
review on the server, and execute an on-line acceptance form.</p>

<p>3. Be responsible for your page's content.</p>

<p>4. Be appropriately responsive to contacts generated through <b>Pit-Stop</b>,
the <b>&quot;Electronic Garage&quot;</b>,</p>

<p><b><font SIZE=+1>Our rights are:</font></b></p>

<p>1. To approve the page content for propriety.</p>

<p>2. To be paid promptly, according to the terms and conditions cited
under Our Fees, below.</p>

<p>3. To remove all material belonging to the client from our server at
the conclusion or non-renewal of the contract. Such material will be discarded.</p>

<p><b><font SIZE=+1>Your rights are:</font></b></p>

<p>1. To 100% availability of your page to the InterNet community.</p>

<p>2. To two (2) Megabytes of storage for your own pages.</p>

<p>3. To <b>Double refund for unavailability of Server</b> - based on whole
hours - Acts of God excluded.</p>

<p>4. To the privacy of data and security of E-mail that your password-required
access provides.</p>

<p><b><font SIZE=+1>Our Fees:</font></b></p>

<p><b>Setup</b></p>

<ul>
<p>Club/Association $ 60.00</p>

<p>Business&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 $100.00</p>
</ul>

<p><b>Hosting Services - Paid in Advance &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Monthly
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Quarterly &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Annually
</p>

<ul>
<p>Club/Association &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$
40.00 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$ 110.00 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$
395.00</p>

<p>Business&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
$ 60.00&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; $ 160.00&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
$ 595.00</p>
</ul>

<p><b>Storage</b> - per Megabyte or increment thereof beyond 2 Megabytes
- $ 2.00/megabyte</p>

<p>Classified&nbsp;s-&nbsp;minimum 3 Months&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
$ 70.00&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; $ 250.00</p>

<ul>
<p>(Limited to 1/2 Meg storage)</p>
</ul>

<p><b>&quot;Hot Links&quot; to existing Pages&nbsp;</b>-&nbsp;minimum 3
Months &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$
70.00 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$ 250.00</p>

<p><b>Maintenance beyond one per month</b> - based on time and hourly rate
currently in effect.</p>

