<p>2. To receive a deposit of one-half the estimated development costs.</p>

<p>3. To be paid promptly, the balance due on delivery of the final designed
pages.</p>

<p><b>Your rights are:</b></p>

<p>1. To timely, faithful, and professionally competent execution of your
design.</p>

<p>2. To final approval and acceptance of our execution before final payment.</p>

