<body text="#FFFF00" bgcolor="#0000FF" link="#FFFF00" vlink="#FFFF00" alink="#FFFF00">

<h1 align=center>Services</h1>

<center><p><b><blink><font SIZE=+1>Our machine shop has over 35 years of
Porsche machining experience.</font></blink></b></p></center>

<center><p><img src="engine.gif" border=0 ></p></center>

<center><p><font SIZE=-1>[ <a href="#914">914 Engines</a> ] [ <a href="#911">911
Engines</a> ] [ <a href="#944">944 Engines</a> ] [ <a href="#other">Other
things we offer...</a> ]</font></p></center>

<h2 align=center>
<hr width="100%" ></h2>

<h2 align=center><a name="914"></a><b>914 Engines </b></h2>

<center><p><b><i>We can build you a E Production <blink>180+</blink> HP
Dyno Tested 914 Engine</i></b></p></center>

<ul>
<li>914 4 cylinder big bore engines (2.7 liter and larger)</li>
</ul>

<ul>
<li>Carburetor conversions.</li>
</ul>

<ul>
<li>6 cylinder conversions.</li>
</ul>

<ul>
<li>Electronic engine management systems.</li>
</ul>

<ul>
<li>911 upright fan and housing for 4 cylinder.</li>
</ul>

<ul>
<li>Crankfire pulley and ignition systems.</li>
</ul>

<ul>
<li>Equal length headers / muffler systems that work.</li>
</ul>

<ul>
<li>We build complete engines for SCCA / Porsche Club series.</li>
</ul>

<p>
<hr width="100%" ></p>

<h2 align=center><a name="911"></a>911 Engines</h2>

<center><p><b><i>We can build you a <blink>600+</blink> HP Dyno Tested
Turbo 911 Engine</i></b></p></center>

<ul>
<li>Big bore conversions up to 3.8 liters.</li>
</ul>

<ul>
<li>Complete Weber carb rebuilding / modifying service.</li>
</ul>

<ul>
<li>We have a large selection of turbo and non-turbo cams to fit you specific
needs.</li>
</ul>

<ul>
<li>Non-turbo Motronic engine packages up to 320 HP.</li>
</ul>

<ul>
<li>Turbo and non-turbo header and muffler systems in mild and stainless
steel.</li>
</ul>

<ul>
<li>Single and multi-throttle turbo and non-turbo engine management 
systems.</li> </ul>

<ul>
<li>Custom intercooler systems.</li>
</ul>

<ul>
<li>KKK &amp; Garrett turbochargers.</li>
</ul>

<p>
<hr width="100%" ></p>

<h2 align=center><a name="944"></a>944 Engines</h2>

<center><p><b><i>We can build you a <blink>425+</blink> HP Dyno Tested
Turbo 944 Engine</i></b></p></center>

<ul>
<li>Big bore / stroker engines up to 3.0 liters (turbo &amp; 
non-turbo)</li> </ul>

<ul>
<li>Big valve head conversions.</li>
</ul>

<ul>
<li>KKK turbo modifications.</li>
</ul>

<ul>
<li>Turbo cams.</li>
</ul>

<ul>
<li>Complete 3&quot; and 4&quot; exhaust systems.</li>
</ul>

<ul>
<li>Big throttle plates.</li>
</ul>

<p>
<hr width="100%" ></p>

<h2 align=center><a name="other"></a>We also offer...</h2>

<ul>
<li><b>Brakes : </b>We can rebuild, modify and install virtually any brake
combination using Porsche, Brembo or other aftermarket components.
We can install twin master cylinder conversions and brake bias valves, 
too.</li> </ul>

<ul>
<li><b>Chassis &amp; Interiors : </b>We install only the best in roll bars
and cages. We can custom bend any rollbar for any application, including
Cabriolet. We can install either Autopower or Safety Devices. If you need
fire protection for your Porsche, we can install the finest fire systems
availble today, either electronic or mechanical.</li>
</ul>

<ul>
<li><b>Engine Machining : </b>Are you planning to build a race engine or
rebuilding your existing engine? Check out some of the things we can help
you with during your engine building process.</li>
</ul>

<ul>
<ul>
<li>Engine cases </li>

<ul>
<li>Deck resurfacing</li>

<li>Line boring</li>

<li>Line honing</li>

<li>Boattail main webs</li>

<li>Oil bypass modifications</li>

<li>Case boring (for larger cylinders)</li>

<li>Timeserting</li>
</ul>
</ul>
</ul>

<ul>
<ul>
<li>Cylinder heads</li>
</ul>

<ul>
<ul>
<li>Resurfacing</li>

<li>Twin plug conversions</li>

<li>Titanium valve / valve train conversions</li>

<li>Intake &amp; exhaust ports larger - port &amp; polish</li>

<li><b>Big</b> valve conversions on 911's, 914's and 944's</li>

<li>Multi-angle valve jobs for street or competition.</li>
</ul>
</ul>
</ul>

<center><p>We can do <b>any custom machining</b> you order. Including flywheels,
suspension components, brake hubs and adapters.</p></center>

<ul>
<li><b>Suspension : </b>We can install and tune your Porsches' suspension
from street to full race. Here are some of the components we use
to get your Porsche to handle like a dream.</li>
</ul>

<ol>
<ul>
<ul>
<li>Weltmeister sway bars</li>

<li>Custom coil over conversions for 911 &amp; 944 alignments</li>

<li>Corner balancing</li>

<li>Special mount conversions</li>

<li>Custom machined Delrin bushings.</li>
</ul>
</ul>
</ol>

<ul>
<li><b>Transmissions : </b>Need a rebuilt or modified transmission for
your Porsche? We do rebuilding for all models. We even rebuild factory
limited slip differentials from 40% to 80%.</li>

<ul>
<ul>
<li>Ring &amp; pinion changes</li>

<li>Individual gear changes</li>

<li>Oil cooler systems installed (electric or mechanical)</li>

<li>Short bellhousing modifications</li>

<li><b>RUF </b>transmission repair</li>
</ul>
</ul>
</ul>

<ul>
<li><b>Wheels : </b>Ask us about our HRE and ETOILE wheels we can install.
</li>
</ul>

<ul>
<ul>
<ul>
<li>Custom fit to your application</li>

<li>We know the widest wheel &amp; tire combinations for all Porsche models</li>
</ul>
</ul>
</ul>

<ul>
<li><b>Other things we do...</b></li>
</ul>

<ul>
<ul>
<ul>
<li>Mig and Tig welding.</li>

<li>Bead blasting.</li>

<li>Powder coating.</li>

<li>Extrude hone (with your parts or use our exchange service)</li>

<li>Fiberglass body panels.</li>

<li>Nitrous oxide kits.</li>
</ul>
</ul>
</ul>

<p>
<hr width="100%" ></p>
