<body text="#FFFF00" bgcolor="#0000FF" link="#FFFF00" vlink="#FFFF00" alink="#FFFF00">

<h1 align=center>Products</h1>

<center><img src="shop2.gif" height=250 width=650></center>

<ul>
<li><b>Heavy Duty Turbo Sump Pumps : </b>Our bolt on pump comes complete
with adapters and all of the fittings. The pump has over three (3) times
the scavaging capability of the stock pump (420 gallons per hour vs 112.5
gph). This pump will enable any turbo to be used without producing
the oil &quot;backup&quot; or smoking problem usually associated with aftermarket
or Garrett conversions. <i>Perfect for twin turbo applications.</i></li>
</ul>

<ul>
<li><b>Crankshaft Pulley for Crankfire Engine Management Systems : </b>Single
or double pulleys for street or track use. Made from 6061 alloy with a
spaceage coating which prolongs its life. All pulleys are available in
standard or small (race) diameter. Come complete with sensor holders and
distributor plug.</li>
</ul>

<ul>
<li><b>Clutch Adapters &amp; Spacers : </b>For 930, 935 and G-50 clutches.
Convert your cast iron clutch package into our aluminum units.</li>
</ul>

<ul>
<li><b>944 Turbo K-27 Installation Kits : </b>This simple kit comes with
the K-27 Turbo, and the bolts and spacers to move the coolant lines out
of the way.</li>
</ul>

<ul>
<li><b>944 Turbo Idle Screws : </b>These idle screws <b><i>are no longer 
availble from Porsche. </i></b>Ours are an exact duplicate of the ones 
which originally came with the car.</li>
</ul>

