<h1 align=center>High Performance Driving Instruction </h1>

<center><p><img src="instruct.gif" border=0 height=250 
width=325></p></center>

<p></p>

<center><img src="racing.gif" alt="racing.gif"></center>

<p></p>

<h2 align=center><i>Would you like to learn how to really drive your 
Porsche?</i></h2>

<center><p><b>Both Keith &amp; Mike at POWERTECH are certfied Porsche Club
of America Driver Education Instructors</b></p></center>

<p>Are you interested in autocrossing, learning how to drive at high speed
or even racing? Both Keith Peare and Mike Daino are instructors with the
<a href="http://www.pit-stop.com/nnjr">Northern New Jersey Region of Porsche
Club of America.</a></p>

