<body text="#FFFF00" bgcolor="#0000FF" link="#FFFF00" vlink="#FFFF00" alink="#FFFF00">

<h1 align=center>Directions to PowerTech </h1>

<center><p><b>Address :</b> 311 W. Main Street. Rockaway, NJ 07866 </p></center>

<center><p><b>Phone :</b> (201)586-3210 <b>Fax :</b> (201)586-6891 </p></center>

<center><p><font SIZE=-1>Conveniently located near Route 80, Exit 37. </font></p></center>

<ul>
<li>Directions From I-80 West or Eastbound : Take exit 37. At the end ofexit
ramp, turn right onto Route 513. Carefully follow signs for route513 to
the center of town. At this point, turn right (still 513) onto WestMain
Street and follow to sign on left for Whimpy Minerals. Make a leftat the
sign (Nichols Drive) and countinue to the bottom of the hill. Proceed straight
ahead into the industrial park. Make first left and then a right just after
the tan building on your right. PowerTech is located in the tan building,
Bays 5 &amp; 6. </li>
</ul>

<ul>
<li>Alternate Route : From Route 46 in the Rockaway area, turn onto ManninoDrive
(this street is between Trend Motors and PriceRite). At the &quot;T&quot;,make
a right into industrial park. Make first left and then a right justafter
the tan building on your right. PowerTech is located in the tan building,
bays 5 &amp; 6. </li>
</ul>

