<H2><CENTER>Welcome to the on-line <BR>Sustainable Agriculture Calendar</CENTER></H2> This calendar provides information on current events relating to sustainable agriculture (with an emphasis on <B>California</B> sustainable agriculture). If you have an event you wish to add to this calendar, please fill out the <U><A HREF="/cgi-win/sarepweb.exe/addevent">add form</A></U>. <P>
