Announcing
The 1997 Farmer-Led Watershed Initiatives Conference

at Good Counsel Academy, Mankato, Minnesota 
February 6-7, 1997

Sponsored by The Institute for Agriculture and Trade Policy and 
The Know Your Watershed Initiative

Who should attend:  
	Farmers, ranchers, staff and leaders of farm, environmental, watershed and commodity organizations, interested local, state and federal agency personnel, extension staff.  

For more information or to register contact:  
	Jim Kleinschmit or Emily Green, IATP, 1313 5th St. SE, Suite 303, Minneapolis, MN  55414;  ph:  612-379-5980; fax:  612-379-5982; email:  water@mtn.org
