</TD></TR>

<TR><TD COLSPAN=12 WIDTH=873><FONT COLOR=#000000>Optimum seeding rates may vary based on local conditions and planting dates. Check with seed supplier for the most appropriate rates. 
<BR>
</FONT>
<P>
