<DOCOLDNO>IA051-000875-B039-257</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.sarep.ucdavis.edu:80/sarep/rfp/bifs_rfp.html 198.31.121.163 19970210144210 text/html 22459
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Mon, 10 Feb 1997 14:39:31 GMT
Server: WebSitePro/1.1g (S/N WPO-13C0)
