Systems Analyst; and <A HREF="/sarep/staff/staff5.html">David Campbell</A>, Economic and Public Policy 
Analyst with contributions from <A HREF="/sarep/staff/staff6.html">David Chaney</A>, Melvin R. George, 
Eric Bradford, the staff and advisory committees of the UC 
Sustainable Agriculture Research and Education Program.</CITE><P> 
 
